text: Phyu Thi (, born 1938) is a Burmese pop singer. Despite her prolific decades- long career, she performed in front of a live audience for the first time in 33 years, during her first concert in March 2013, at the National Theatre of Yangon. She has released 14 albums. == Discography == * Ten Million Miles (မိုင်ပေါင်းကုဋေ) (1980) == References == Category:1938 births Category:Living people Category:Burmese female singers
